word_group.brief_definition: 宏大的计划；雄心勃勃的计划
雄心勃勃的目标；志存高远的目标

bilingual.source: Her ambitious plan is to become the youngest CEO of the company.
bilingual.target: 她野心勃勃的计划是成为公司最年轻的CEO（Chief Executive Officer，首席执行官）。

bilingual.source: He's a very smart and ambitious guy.
bilingual.target: 他是一个非常聪明且野心勃勃的家伙。

bilingual.source: He had a reputation of an ambitious firebrand.
bilingual.target: 大家把他誉为一个野心勃勃的煽动家.

bilingual.source: He had a reputation of an ambitious firebrand .
bilingual.target: 大家把他誉为一个野心勃勃的煽动家。

bilingual.source: They ventured on an ambitious program of reform.
bilingual.target: 他们冒然采取一项野心勃勃的改革计画.

bilingual.source: I'm ambitious too, but I have to be objective.
bilingual.target: 我也是野心勃勃的，但是我必须脚踏实地。

bilingual.source: You strike me as being a very ambitious person.
bilingual.target: 我觉得你是一个野心勃勃的人。

bilingual.source: The feisty, ambitious wannabes, grew bored and restless.
bilingual.target: 这群不安分的 、 野心勃勃的“想要”们变得烦躁不安、心绪不定起来.

bilingual.source: The candidate qualified his rivals as ambitious selfseekers.
bilingual.target: 竞选者将他的对手说成是野心勃勃的利己主义者.

bilingual.source: The White House was a magnet for more than ambitious politicians.
bilingual.target: 白宫是一块磁石,不光是对野心勃勃的政治家有吸引力.

yingyinNormal.en: You're too ambitious for your own good.
I like him. He's a good guy. He's ambitious.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我挺喜欢他，他人不错，很有野心。

yingyinNormal.en: I was an ambitious young warrior leading a great army. And fighting by my side was Kai. My closest friend.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我曾是一名雄心勃勃的年轻战士，带领一支伟大的军队，与我并肩作战的就是天煞，我最亲密的朋友。

yingyinNormal.en: And that will take Elon closer to a more ambitious goal: To help send crews to establish a colony on Mars.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这会使埃隆向着更远大目标迈进：帮助宇航员在火星上建立一个殖民地。

yingyinNormal.en: Millions will be watching around the harbor and across the nation on TV, so Wilson has devised an ambitious firework to celebrate the incoming year.
yingyinNormal.zh: 数百万观众在现场和电视上观看烟花表演，因此，威尔森有个雄心勃勃的设计，以迎接新年。

yingyinNormal.en: To create a nationwide web of tracks, the Federal Government launched one of the most ambitious and expensive infrastructure projects in human history.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为制造全国铁路线的网络，联邦政府启动人类史上最具野心，也是最昂贵的基础设施计划。

yingyinNormal.en: It's not him, it's a her. Francine Tenaka. And if you don't know who Tenaka is, there's no reason you should know who Brad Petite is, or that he's ambitious or a good guy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不是他，是她。弗朗辛·谭纳卡，如果你不知道谭纳卡是谁，那你根本不应该认识布拉德·帕蒂特，也不该知道他人怎么样，是否有野心。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 在任何情况下，这都是雄心勃勃的，但在这个有分歧而又不平等的社会中，这两个理想可能会出现直接地冲突。
